(122, 1, '2013-12-06 06:19:21', '2013-12-06 06:19:21', '<a href="http://landing.mckansys.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/market1.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-123" alt="market1" src="http://landing.mckansys.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/market1.jpg" width="800" height="348" /></a>\r\n<table border="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://landing.mckansys.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/market2.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-124" alt="market2" src="http://landing.mckansys.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/market2.jpg" width="405" height="348" /></a></td>\r\n<td><span style="color: #129793;">Market Research offers research service on both D</span><span style="color: #129793;">emand and Supply sides across all industries.</span>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #129793;">Through our proprietary methodology, we help clients understand market sizing, market share, and competitive landscape of studied market.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #129793;">For demand side, our methodology points out market characteristics, us</span><span style="color: #129793;">age and behavior study,  customer satisfaction, customer loyalty, and service evaluation.</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td> <a href="http://landing.mckansys.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/market3.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-130" alt="market3" src="http://landing.mckansys.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/market3.jpg" width="405" height="348" /></a></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #129793;">An intermediate level of Capability Building named Market Analysis &amp; Modeling service, supporting marketing and technology strategists, CMO, CTO, and CIO to understand Market Landscape and Market Dynamics.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #129793;"> </span><span style="color: #129793;">Market Analysis &amp; Modeling service focuses on analyzing information on top